{"tid":254921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剛剛食譚仔，點知⋯⋯⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-05-23T13:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T14:10:50.000Z","uid":44111,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef5d54a7b9719d63f783b4c10c8a2dc7dccb717","tid":254921,"uid":44111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"剛剛去食譚仔，原本我叫魚腐墨丸，跟住呢頭落完單，轉頭1分鐘都無，呀姐就擺左碗嘢喺我枱頭，我心諗咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，跟住我掛住望手機，就無理碗野裡面喺咩，就老閪咁食左幾啖，跟住我望望，再周圍搵碗野，咦...屌你腩肉嚟嘅，跟住叫呀姐換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，望住呀姐攞住碗嘢擺返喺出菜位，過左一陣攞返魚腐墨丸比我咪食囉，跟住我多眼望吓個出菜位，我之前果碗仲喺到，突然有另一個呀姐，攞住呢碗野，比左第二枱客，仲要同個客講唔好意思等咁耐，個毒撚仲同呀姐講唔緊要啦，跟住喺咁食，我當堂差啲忍唔住想噴出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0401c87df8056a8c017a4fd9d788f927677cd5e","tid":254921,"uid":113733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b6e5ab0baae6508c5b1fb0f0f97c28cd27fe79","tid":254921,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"邊間，開名"},{"pid":"1201d548efcd25a4be3c707ed243e68fecdf9bd5","tid":254921,"uid":65186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"我想話，飲食業好平常"},{"pid":"e73b6c508e51a4452c817cdf2df81bbe45f21c0f","tid":254921,"uid":44111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間，開名</blockquote><br />\n唔通....個毒撚係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff95432c483ebd3fee4c87bb91afa05a12c4a03","tid":254921,"uid":44111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想話，飲食業好平常</blockquote><br />\n係都唔緊要，但都扮野攞入廚房行個圈啦"},{"pid":"27c9187ca826dda30ac4fa63eb8f8a7e92cd0d9e","tid":254921,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":